1
00:01:28,768 --> 00:01:33,760
=Lost You Forever S1=

2
00:01:33,984 --> 00:01:36,544
=Episode 31=

3
00:01:46,618 --> 00:01:47,137
Your Highness.

4
00:01:49,257 --> 00:01:50,817
I tried three tortures on him.

5
00:01:51,457 --> 00:01:52,978
He couldn't take it and wanted to die.

6
00:01:53,457 --> 00:01:56,378
But he still hasn't
named his accomplices.

7
00:02:02,817 --> 00:02:06,058
I killed your little sister.

8
00:02:06,738 --> 00:02:11,417
Take my life as you wish.

9
00:02:11,818 --> 00:02:12,938
You did it alone?

10
00:02:13,538 --> 00:02:15,178
You really speak highly of yourself.

11
00:02:15,378 --> 00:02:17,857
They must have agreed
to let him take all the blame

12
00:02:18,777 --> 00:02:19,697
before the action.

13
00:02:20,497 --> 00:02:23,497
His clan has been wiped out.

14
00:02:24,617 --> 00:02:26,337
Even if the two kings are furious,

15
00:02:27,018 --> 00:02:30,258
they can only kill him.

16
00:02:31,137 --> 00:02:35,137
I have no family whatsoever.

17
00:02:35,658 --> 00:02:38,738
If you want my life, take it.

18
00:02:39,178 --> 00:02:43,217
You have no family whatsoever?

19
00:02:45,057 --> 00:02:48,137
I bet countless people died
trying to save you

20
00:02:48,658 --> 00:02:50,178
from Chi Chen's blade.

21
00:02:51,458 --> 00:02:55,857
Do you really have the nerves
to terminate the Mu family here?

22
00:02:58,378 --> 00:02:59,378
What do you mean?

23
00:02:59,658 --> 00:03:00,417
Xiaoxiao.

24
00:03:03,738 --> 00:03:06,057
When he was living
with his relatives, the Shen family,

25
00:03:06,417 --> 00:03:08,098
his maid Liu'er was kicked out

26
00:03:08,378 --> 00:03:10,538
of the mansion due to adultery

27
00:03:10,898 --> 00:03:12,697
and soon gave birth to a boy.

28
00:03:13,217 --> 00:03:14,898
You've been careful enough

29
00:03:15,977 --> 00:03:18,258
to avoid contact with them,

30
00:03:18,697 --> 00:03:21,137
but I still discovered something.

31
00:03:22,098 --> 00:03:23,898
The son of this maid

32
00:03:24,818 --> 00:03:26,697
must be yours.

33
00:03:28,258 --> 00:03:30,658
You can remain silent and die.

34
00:03:32,938 --> 00:03:34,337
I will send your son

35
00:03:35,137 --> 00:03:38,178
to reunite with the entire Mu family.

36
00:03:46,658 --> 00:03:48,497
You're a devil!

37
00:03:48,818 --> 00:03:50,658
You're a lunatic!

38
00:03:50,818 --> 00:03:52,217
You killed my little sister.

39
00:03:53,018 --> 00:03:54,898
I swear I'll claim your life!

40
00:03:56,617 --> 00:03:58,458
But if you tell me one thing,

41
00:04:00,178 --> 00:04:01,857
I will leave your son out of it.

42
00:04:04,898 --> 00:04:06,258
I killed your little sister.

43
00:04:08,258 --> 00:04:09,018
Other than that,

44
00:04:11,217 --> 00:04:12,617
I know nothing.

45
00:04:12,777 --> 00:04:14,298
I know you won't betray your partners.

46
00:04:15,697 --> 00:04:16,457
I just want to know

47
00:04:17,098 --> 00:04:18,658
why you wanted to kill Xiaoyao.

48
00:04:20,578 --> 00:04:21,497
Just tell me that

49
00:04:22,858 --> 00:04:24,217
and I'll spare your son.

50
00:04:26,698 --> 00:04:29,418
You have some time to think it through.

51
00:04:31,698 --> 00:04:32,818
Don't try to commit suicide.

52
00:04:35,617 --> 00:04:36,858
Think about your son.

53
00:04:55,098 --> 00:04:55,777
Xiaoyao.

54
00:04:57,538 --> 00:04:58,418
Xiaoyao.

55
00:05:06,538 --> 00:05:07,177
Your Highness.

56
00:05:08,737 --> 00:05:09,578
What's wrong?

57
00:05:10,698 --> 00:05:11,818
Mu Fei wants to see you.

58
00:05:12,497 --> 00:05:14,337
But he wants Mr. Fenglong there, too.

59
00:05:14,538 --> 00:05:15,457
I see.

60
00:05:22,897 --> 00:05:23,858
I can tell you

61
00:05:23,858 --> 00:05:25,057
why I killed your sister.

62
00:05:27,138 --> 00:05:28,258
But you have to promise

63
00:05:29,457 --> 00:05:31,017
that you'll never hurt my son.

64
00:05:31,297 --> 00:05:32,658
As long as you tell the truth,

65
00:05:32,978 --> 00:05:34,057
I won't hurt him.

66
00:05:35,818 --> 00:05:38,337
I don't trust anyone from Xiyan.

67
00:05:40,617 --> 00:05:42,418
I want to hear you say that

68
00:05:43,378 --> 00:05:46,658
no one shall ever hurt my son.

69
00:05:47,177 --> 00:05:48,938
As long as you tell Cang Xuan the truth,

70
00:05:49,538 --> 00:05:51,858
I promise no one shall hurt your son

71
00:05:51,858 --> 00:05:53,177
for what you've done.

72
00:05:55,578 --> 00:05:57,138
You must be resenting me

73
00:05:57,658 --> 00:06:00,897
for causing so much trouble
for the clans in the Central Plains.

74
00:06:03,337 --> 00:06:04,777
But I had to kill her.

75
00:06:07,538 --> 00:06:09,737
Because she's not
the Great Princess of Haoling at all.

76
00:06:10,538 --> 00:06:12,297
She is the daughter of Chi Chen.

77
00:06:12,538 --> 00:06:13,378
- No way.
- No way.

78
00:06:16,617 --> 00:06:18,858
I've seen that demon's eyes in person.

79
00:06:22,177 --> 00:06:23,217
I can't be wrong.

80
00:06:30,737 --> 00:06:32,177
After I saw the fake princess,

81
00:06:32,978 --> 00:06:34,737
I was filled with hatred and rage.

82
00:06:35,617 --> 00:06:37,538
But I still investigated her carefully.

83
00:06:38,457 --> 00:06:40,418
I even consulted
Fifth King and Seventh King.

84
00:06:41,337 --> 00:06:43,497
The demon Chi Chen annihilated my clan.

85
00:06:44,017 --> 00:06:47,457
I will never forget how he looks.

86
00:06:47,978 --> 00:06:49,378
It just occurred to me

87
00:06:49,858 --> 00:06:51,337
that the Great Princess of Haoling

88
00:06:51,737 --> 00:06:53,177
reminded me a bit of Chi Chen.

89
00:06:53,497 --> 00:06:55,938
And I've heard rumors
between Princess General

90
00:06:56,337 --> 00:06:57,938
and that demon.

91
00:06:58,658 --> 00:06:59,297
Therefore,

92
00:07:00,258 --> 00:07:02,378
I came to seek your confirmation.

93
00:07:02,777 --> 00:07:03,457
What rumors?

94
00:07:03,578 --> 00:07:06,497
Your Highnesses,
you lived through that period.

95
00:07:07,138 --> 00:07:10,457
Have you ever heard of the affair
between Princess General and Chi Chen?

96
00:07:10,938 --> 00:07:14,698
To be honest,
there were indeed rumors saying that

97
00:07:15,098 --> 00:07:16,497
Xiling Heng and Chi Chen...

98
00:07:17,938 --> 00:07:18,617
However,

99
00:07:19,138 --> 00:07:21,378
it was before she married
the King of Haoling.

100
00:07:21,858 --> 00:07:24,938
So Princess General
and Chi Chen indeed...

101
00:07:25,017 --> 00:07:25,858
There's no such thing.

102
00:07:27,258 --> 00:07:30,138
Brother, Father has forbidden
anyone to discuss this.

103
00:07:31,418 --> 00:07:32,177
Don't you remember?

104
00:07:34,538 --> 00:07:36,337
Fine, I won't discuss it.

105
00:07:36,818 --> 00:07:39,297
Those are just random rumors.

106
00:07:40,098 --> 00:07:41,138
Don't take them seriously.

107
00:07:41,578 --> 00:07:44,978
Xiling Heng divorced
the King of Haoling for other reasons.

108
00:07:45,617 --> 00:07:48,138
It had nothing to do with Chi Chen.

109
00:07:51,578 --> 00:07:55,818
Although they were
extremely reluctant to talk about it,

110
00:07:56,818 --> 00:07:59,497
I was sure I was right.

111
00:08:01,337 --> 00:08:03,497
She was the daughter of Chi Chen.

112
00:08:03,858 --> 00:08:05,418
Nonsense.

113
00:08:05,938 --> 00:08:07,818
Before Auntie left for war,
she had told me

114
00:08:08,297 --> 00:08:09,378
to ask the King of Haoling

115
00:08:09,818 --> 00:08:11,457
for help if anything went wrong.

116
00:08:11,938 --> 00:08:13,897
If she had betrayed him,

117
00:08:14,177 --> 00:08:15,378
why was he nice enough

118
00:08:16,098 --> 00:08:19,578
to educate me and protect me in Haoling?

119
00:08:20,017 --> 00:08:20,578
Yeah.

120
00:08:21,217 --> 00:08:21,978
Mu Fei.

121
00:08:22,578 --> 00:08:23,777
Think about it.

122
00:08:24,457 --> 00:08:25,897
King of Haoling is so shrewd.

123
00:08:26,297 --> 00:08:27,457
You can find the truth.

124
00:08:27,858 --> 00:08:29,378
But he can't?

125
00:08:30,177 --> 00:08:31,818
If he had doubts about Xiaoyao,

126
00:08:32,218 --> 00:08:34,617
why would he hold
such a grand worship ceremony

127
00:08:35,338 --> 00:08:37,938
to show people in Dahuang
how much he loved Xiaoyao?

128
00:08:39,417 --> 00:08:40,898
Did I really kill the wrong person?

129
00:08:48,578 --> 00:08:49,057
No.

130
00:08:49,977 --> 00:08:50,657
No way.

131
00:08:52,778 --> 00:08:54,138
I've seen those eyes.

132
00:08:55,138 --> 00:08:56,338
I can't be wrong.

133
00:08:56,737 --> 00:08:57,938
There's no way I'm wrong.

134
00:08:58,097 --> 00:09:00,737
It's too late
even if you realize your mistake.

135
00:09:02,258 --> 00:09:03,737
You hurt Xiaoyao.

136
00:09:05,378 --> 00:09:07,417
You will pay with your life.

137
00:09:23,417 --> 00:09:25,018
I sacrificed one life to save you.

138
00:09:25,698 --> 00:09:26,977
If you dare to die,

139
00:09:28,018 --> 00:09:32,297
I will chop you up
and feed you to the fish.

140
00:09:45,818 --> 00:09:47,417
(The nine-tailed fox also said)

141
00:09:47,938 --> 00:09:50,497
(that my mom had been
having an affair with Chi Chen.)

142
00:09:51,818 --> 00:09:54,938
They had kept it a secret
from everyone, including my father.

143
00:09:57,138 --> 00:09:59,177
If he had found out about it,

144
00:09:59,778 --> 00:10:02,057
(he would have gotten rid of me.)

145
00:10:12,737 --> 00:10:14,417
Still mad about what Mu Fei said?

146
00:10:15,177 --> 00:10:17,097
Nobody would believe in such nonsense.

147
00:10:17,297 --> 00:10:20,258
I hope what he said
can remain between us

148
00:10:20,578 --> 00:10:21,778
not only because

149
00:10:21,778 --> 00:10:24,338
it affects the reputation
of the King of Haoling and my auntie,

150
00:10:24,578 --> 00:10:26,378
but also because my dear uncles

151
00:10:26,657 --> 00:10:30,138
wanted to use the clans
in the Central Plains to kill Xiaoyao.

152
00:10:30,857 --> 00:10:31,857
I understand.

153
00:10:32,537 --> 00:10:33,938
Xiaoyao is prestigious.

154
00:10:34,617 --> 00:10:36,258
If it's not handled properly,

155
00:10:36,977 --> 00:10:39,417
the King of Xiyan may blame it
on the Central Plains

156
00:10:40,417 --> 00:10:42,737
and put it into turbulence again.

157
00:10:44,378 --> 00:10:45,938
For the peace of the Central Plains,

158
00:10:46,258 --> 00:10:48,938
I will be careful and remain silent.

159
00:10:49,097 --> 00:10:51,497
Since we know
why Mu Fei wanted Xiaoyao dead,

160
00:10:52,578 --> 00:10:54,338
it's easy to find his accomplices.

161
00:10:55,857 --> 00:10:58,177
Chi Chen wiped out many clans,

162
00:10:59,057 --> 00:11:01,177
but not many of them have members left.

163
00:11:01,578 --> 00:11:03,218
First, they need to know Mu Fei well

164
00:11:03,737 --> 00:11:05,818
to trust each other
in this assassination.

165
00:11:06,138 --> 00:11:07,737
Second, they should practice

166
00:11:08,338 --> 00:11:10,138
Water Spirit and Wood Spirit.

167
00:11:11,497 --> 00:11:14,138
And I feel that one of them is a woman.

168
00:11:14,898 --> 00:11:17,778
Only a woman can manage
to separate Xinyue and Xiaoyao

169
00:11:18,297 --> 00:11:20,297
and stop the secret guards
I sent around Xiaoyao

170
00:11:21,177 --> 00:11:23,497
without attracting attention.

171
00:11:25,177 --> 00:11:26,537
You've got a point.

172
00:11:28,097 --> 00:11:29,297
With all this information,

173
00:11:30,258 --> 00:11:32,297
I bet you already know who did it.

174
00:11:32,617 --> 00:11:34,018
Come to Chenrong Mansion tonight.

175
00:11:34,778 --> 00:11:36,537
Xinyue and I will
have an answer for you.

176
00:11:37,258 --> 00:11:37,898
Alright.

177
00:13:29,338 --> 00:13:30,977
Xinyue took me to the plum blossom wood,

178
00:13:31,778 --> 00:13:32,898
and I was assassinated.

179
00:13:34,417 --> 00:13:35,617
Where am I?

180
00:13:36,617 --> 00:13:37,898
Am I already dead?

181
00:14:00,857 --> 00:14:02,497
So I can't leave my body?

182
00:14:04,537 --> 00:14:07,177
Does Cang Xuan know how I am?

183
00:14:08,458 --> 00:14:09,857
He must be worried sick.

184
00:14:20,938 --> 00:14:22,737
Brother, it's a good opportunity.

185
00:14:24,297 --> 00:14:25,338
I know it's an opportunity.

186
00:14:26,338 --> 00:14:27,857
But Cang Xuan

187
00:14:27,977 --> 00:14:29,537
will have to make a decision.

188
00:14:35,297 --> 00:14:36,138
Found the culprit?

189
00:14:40,177 --> 00:14:40,898
After investigation,

190
00:14:41,258 --> 00:14:43,218
we confirmed that
there were four culprits.

191
00:14:43,417 --> 00:14:44,458
Apart from Mu Fei,

192
00:14:44,898 --> 00:14:47,458
there are orphans of
the Shen, Zhan, and Jin families,

193
00:14:47,778 --> 00:14:49,818
namely Shen Zhong,
Zhan Xueling, and Jin Yuejian.

194
00:14:52,778 --> 00:14:53,578
Thank you.

195
00:14:54,378 --> 00:14:56,578
Cang Xuan, one more thing.

196
00:14:56,898 --> 00:14:57,578
What is it?

197
00:15:00,018 --> 00:15:02,417
The Fan and the Zheng families
came to see me

198
00:15:02,898 --> 00:15:04,698
and pleaded
for Zhan Xueling and Jin Yuejian.

199
00:15:05,057 --> 00:15:07,617
Zhan Xueling is Mr. Fan's fiance.

200
00:15:08,057 --> 00:15:10,018
They grew up together
as childhood sweethearts

201
00:15:10,177 --> 00:15:11,778
and would get married in three months.

202
00:15:12,018 --> 00:15:15,977
Jin Yuejian was engaged to the daughter
of the Zheng family at a young age.

203
00:15:16,338 --> 00:15:17,617
They've always been close.

204
00:15:22,338 --> 00:15:24,338
The Fan and Zheng families said

205
00:15:25,297 --> 00:15:27,898
that as long as you went easy
on Zhan Xueling and Jin Yuejian,

206
00:15:28,458 --> 00:15:32,657
their families would pay back
by showing support. I...

207
00:15:36,537 --> 00:15:37,218
I...

208
00:15:40,778 --> 00:15:43,578
suggest you think twice.

209
00:15:47,258 --> 00:15:48,898
That's also my opinion.

210
00:15:49,338 --> 00:15:51,097
You need talents at this moment.

211
00:15:51,737 --> 00:15:53,578
If you kill Zhan Xueling
and Jin Yuejian,

212
00:15:54,138 --> 00:15:56,417
the two clans of the six
will turn against you.

213
00:15:57,258 --> 00:15:57,938
It's not worth it.

214
00:15:58,497 --> 00:15:59,977
That's right.

215
00:16:01,218 --> 00:16:03,537
Cang Xuan, to achieve great success,

216
00:16:04,097 --> 00:16:05,698
you must know what to do

217
00:16:06,057 --> 00:16:07,097
and what not to do.

218
00:16:08,977 --> 00:16:10,297
The harm to Xiaoyao

219
00:16:10,898 --> 00:16:12,378
can't be undone even if you kill them.

220
00:16:12,977 --> 00:16:15,578
You can only vent your anger,
which is pointless.

221
00:16:16,097 --> 00:16:17,177
But if you spare them,

222
00:16:17,737 --> 00:16:20,737
they will be your supporters
and help you achieve great things.

223
00:16:35,417 --> 00:16:36,617
Good point.

224
00:16:41,018 --> 00:16:42,938
Let me tell you
a story from my childhood.

225
00:16:44,297 --> 00:16:45,417
I was quite young.

226
00:16:47,378 --> 00:16:49,338
My parents left to fight in the war,

227
00:16:49,857 --> 00:16:51,218
the one against your grandpa,

228
00:16:51,938 --> 00:16:53,537
Chenrong Yanzhuan.

229
00:16:54,818 --> 00:16:55,458
One day,

230
00:16:57,497 --> 00:16:59,458
my mother and auntie suddenly came back

231
00:17:01,338 --> 00:17:03,338
with the news that
my father died in the war.

232
00:17:08,137 --> 00:17:11,858
I saw my granny,
my auntie, and my mother

233
00:17:14,417 --> 00:17:16,537
hugging each other and crying.

234
00:17:18,177 --> 00:17:19,897
Granny was the founding queen of Xiyan

235
00:17:21,297 --> 00:17:23,137
who used to fight alongside Grandpa.

236
00:17:24,098 --> 00:17:25,777
My mother was the wise leader

237
00:17:26,057 --> 00:17:27,098
of the Ruoshui Clan.

238
00:17:28,458 --> 00:17:31,938
My auntie was the Princess General
who became known throughout Dahuang

239
00:17:32,458 --> 00:17:33,777
and died defending the kingdom.

240
00:17:34,417 --> 00:17:37,618
The three of them were
the toughest women I'd known.

241
00:17:41,578 --> 00:17:42,978
But at that moment,

242
00:17:44,338 --> 00:17:46,417
they cried their hearts out

243
00:17:47,578 --> 00:17:49,098
like they lost all hope in life

244
00:17:50,938 --> 00:17:52,537
and didn't know what lay ahead.

245
00:17:55,777 --> 00:17:57,297
It was heartbreaking.

246
00:18:02,578 --> 00:18:03,698
At that moment,

247
00:18:06,177 --> 00:18:07,578
I swore to myself that

248
00:18:10,297 --> 00:18:12,297
I would be strong,

249
00:18:13,338 --> 00:18:15,777
much stronger than the King of Xiyan.

250
00:18:18,057 --> 00:18:19,777
I have to protect them.

251
00:18:23,858 --> 00:18:26,338
I will never let my grandma,
my auntie, and my mom

252
00:18:28,578 --> 00:18:31,017
weep helplessly
out of the deepest grief.

253
00:18:34,897 --> 00:18:35,578
But...

254
00:18:47,698 --> 00:18:48,498
But...

255
00:18:52,098 --> 00:18:53,738
They didn't see me grow up.

256
00:18:59,698 --> 00:19:01,377
I want to protect my family.

257
00:19:03,017 --> 00:19:04,578
That's why I'm eager to grow up

258
00:19:05,137 --> 00:19:06,338
and gain power.

259
00:19:07,978 --> 00:19:10,738
That's why I want to
achieve greater things than my grandpa.

260
00:19:13,498 --> 00:19:15,177
If I choose to let go

261
00:19:16,818 --> 00:19:19,177
of those who hurt Xiaoyao to gain power,

262
00:19:20,618 --> 00:19:23,177
I'd be betraying my younger self
in the Zhaoyun Hall.

263
00:19:25,897 --> 00:19:27,098
As you said,

264
00:19:28,698 --> 00:19:30,777
there are things we can do
and things we can't do.

265
00:19:31,698 --> 00:19:33,098
But no matter what,

266
00:19:33,618 --> 00:19:34,377
we shouldn't

267
00:19:35,338 --> 00:19:37,377
betray ourselves.

268
00:19:40,218 --> 00:19:42,338
When you try to talk me out of it,

269
00:19:44,098 --> 00:19:47,978
has it crossed your mind that
if I give up on Xiaoyao for some reason,

