I'm sorry. Please.

547
00:36:40,018 --> 00:36:40,857
Please come back.

548
00:36:41,817 --> 00:36:43,498
I'm even lonelier without you.

549
00:36:43,738 --> 00:36:45,137
Who's going to talk to me?

550
00:36:51,538 --> 00:36:52,218
Your Highness.

551
00:36:53,177 --> 00:36:56,617
Do you think the Poinciana Wood will
resemble the one on the Zhaoyun Peak?

552
00:36:58,978 --> 00:36:59,857
Eventually.

553
00:37:01,577 --> 00:37:02,458
That's great.

554
00:37:03,018 --> 00:37:05,577
Princess will be so happy
once she's back.

555
00:37:06,177 --> 00:37:07,978
She has always loved Poinciana trees.

556
00:37:08,577 --> 00:37:10,657
Once they're fully grown,

557
00:37:11,978 --> 00:37:14,897
I'll make her a swing
just like the one on the Zhaoyun Peak.

558
00:37:15,298 --> 00:37:16,258
Even better.

559
00:37:17,298 --> 00:37:19,657
You'll push the swing for her

560
00:37:20,058 --> 00:37:21,377
just like when you were kids.

561
00:37:29,458 --> 00:37:30,897
- Your Highness.
- Did you see him?

562
00:37:31,778 --> 00:37:32,817
Xiang Liu is hard to track.

563
00:37:33,018 --> 00:37:34,097
I didn't see him.

564
00:37:34,337 --> 00:37:36,298
I simply left
the spiritual medicines there.

565
00:37:36,778 --> 00:37:38,778
He left you a message.

566
00:37:41,792 --> 00:37:45,056
(No longer in critical condition.
But she hasn't woken up.)

567
00:37:47,298 --> 00:37:49,458
Your Highness,
is it news about Princess?

568
00:37:49,498 --> 00:37:51,498
How is she? Has she woken up?

569
00:37:52,177 --> 00:37:53,617
She hasn't woken up yet,

570
00:37:54,377 --> 00:37:56,778
but she's no longer
in critical condition.

571
00:37:58,337 --> 00:37:59,177
That's good.

572
00:37:59,617 --> 00:38:00,298
Great.

573
00:38:00,377 --> 00:38:01,577
How's Tushan Jing doing?

574
00:38:02,058 --> 00:38:04,018
Master Qiuqing
is getting worse and worse.

575
00:38:04,738 --> 00:38:06,978
Grand Madam of Tushan
asked the King of Haoling

576
00:38:07,298 --> 00:38:09,337
for permission to send
Master Qingqiu to Guixu.

577
00:38:09,538 --> 00:38:12,538
However, he got weaker and weaker

578
00:38:12,778 --> 00:38:14,298
once he left Zhiyi.

579
00:38:14,897 --> 00:38:16,498
Things didn't look right, so they

580
00:38:16,577 --> 00:38:18,112
sent him back to Chenrong Mansion.

581
00:38:18,298 --> 00:38:20,377
Send someone to keep an eye on him.

582
00:38:20,657 --> 00:38:22,698
He fell sick because of Xiaoyao.

583
00:38:23,177 --> 00:38:24,778
She wouldn't want to see him sick.

584
00:38:25,698 --> 00:38:26,258
Understood.

585
00:39:18,738 --> 00:39:20,137
You have such an amazing puppet.

586
00:39:21,897 --> 00:39:22,817
I lost.

587
00:39:23,177 --> 00:39:24,978
A visit from an old acquaintance.

588
00:39:25,938 --> 00:39:27,458
Chenrong Mountain is well-guarded.

589
00:39:28,577 --> 00:39:29,417
How did you enter?

590
00:39:29,938 --> 00:39:31,617
Evil deeds bring self-destruction.

591
00:39:32,218 --> 00:39:34,137
I'm not the only one who wants you dead.

592
00:39:34,538 --> 00:39:35,897
Try to stay alive first.

593
00:39:41,577 --> 00:39:42,258
Let him go.

594
00:39:42,978 --> 00:39:44,377
Your Highness, don't.

595
00:39:45,498 --> 00:39:46,018
Let him go.

596
00:39:55,337 --> 00:39:56,097
You can go now.

597
00:40:00,417 --> 00:40:01,458
If you don't kill me today,

598
00:40:02,417 --> 00:40:03,938
I'll kill you some other day.

599
00:40:04,458 --> 00:40:05,897
Then you should be careful

600
00:40:06,738 --> 00:40:08,058
not to be caught again.

601
00:40:31,817 --> 00:40:33,298
Take the front door.

602
00:41:07,817 --> 00:41:08,577
What for?

603
00:41:12,177 --> 00:41:14,417
This well-forged dagger

604
00:41:14,857 --> 00:41:16,377
is made to take out hearts.

605
00:41:18,298 --> 00:41:19,498
It's named Heart Appreciator.

606
00:41:21,458 --> 00:41:22,857
This is Bone Smashing Hammer.

607
00:41:29,058 --> 00:41:30,577
This is Burned Goose Palm

608
00:41:31,018 --> 00:41:32,577
named after a dish.

609
00:41:33,137 --> 00:41:34,218
But it burns human feet.

610
00:41:34,978 --> 00:41:36,778
Your evil hypocrite

611
00:41:37,218 --> 00:41:38,577
racked your brain

612
00:41:39,018 --> 00:41:40,897
to come up with
these horrendous tortures.

613
00:41:41,458 --> 00:41:42,857
It's a pity that I'm incapable

614
00:41:43,218 --> 00:41:45,258
of killing you
for the benefit of the people.

615
00:41:46,298 --> 00:41:46,938
Say no more.

616
00:41:47,577 --> 00:41:49,778
Kill me as you wish.

617
00:41:50,458 --> 00:41:52,738
You also think of someone
who invented these tools

618
00:41:53,738 --> 00:41:56,258
as a devil that deserves to be killed.

619
00:41:57,137 --> 00:41:58,577
Anyone would pleasantly

620
00:41:59,018 --> 00:42:00,177
kill a maniac beast.

621
00:42:01,018 --> 00:42:02,897
The Lord of Zhiyi 200 years ago

622
00:42:03,657 --> 00:42:05,377
