of innocent people in prison

625
00:42:10,337 --> 00:42:11,377
with false accusations.

626
00:42:12,137 --> 00:42:14,058
The current Lord of Zhiyi gave the order

627
00:42:15,218 --> 00:42:18,137
to stop using most of these tools.

628
00:42:18,897 --> 00:42:22,097
So don't worry about being tortured.

629
00:42:23,698 --> 00:42:25,657
The previous Lord of Zhiyi?

630
00:42:29,738 --> 00:42:31,617
His mother was from the Xiyan clan.

631
00:42:32,778 --> 00:42:36,657
His father was from Haoling Xihe Squad.

632
00:42:39,817 --> 00:42:41,218
His name was Xuan Ting.

633
00:42:43,538 --> 00:42:45,738
Utter nonsense! No way!

634
00:42:46,577 --> 00:42:47,337
Untie him.

635
00:42:50,538 --> 00:42:51,097
Give it to him.

636
00:43:03,018 --> 00:43:06,177
These are Xuan Ting's case files
on the people he tortured.

637
00:43:07,137 --> 00:43:10,498
He listed the specific types
of tortures he used

638
00:43:11,298 --> 00:43:12,738
and the victims' reactions.

639
00:43:18,258 --> 00:43:19,657
It was a coincidence that

640
00:43:20,938 --> 00:43:22,817
Grandpa assigned this case
to me back then.

641
00:43:25,337 --> 00:43:27,337
I never regretted
killing your big brother.

642
00:43:27,778 --> 00:43:28,817
Because he was

643
00:43:29,258 --> 00:43:30,698
a high official

644
00:43:31,298 --> 00:43:33,498
who adopted tortures on innocent people

645
00:43:33,698 --> 00:43:35,577
and killed tens of thousands of them.

646
00:43:37,258 --> 00:43:38,458
He deserved it.

647
00:43:40,938 --> 00:43:42,577
If you think I've made a mistake,

648
00:43:43,298 --> 00:43:44,897
go on with the assassinations.

649
